{"name": "odoo-addon-product-secondary-unit", "metadata": {"name": "odoo-addon-product-secondary-unit", "version": "17.0.1.0.0.3", "classifiers": ["Development Status :: 5 - Production/Stable", "Framework :: Odoo", "Framework :: Odoo :: 17.0", "License :: OSI Approved :: GNU Affero General Public License v3", "Programming Language :: Python"], "home_page": "https://github.com/OCA/product-attribute", "license": "AGPL-3", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["odoo"], "summary": "Set a secondary unit per product", "upload_time": 1722312063}, "documentation": ["---\nsubstitutions:\n  badge1: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/maturity-Production%2FStable-green.png\n    :alt: Production/Stable\n    :target: https://odoo-community.org/page/development-status\n    ```\n  badge2: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/licence-AGPL--3-blue.png\n    :alt: 'License: AGPL-3'\n    :target: http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl-3.0-standalone.html\n    ```\n  badge3: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/github-OCA%2Fproduct--attribute-lightgray.png?logo=github\n    :alt: OCA/product-attribute\n    :target: https://github.com/OCA/product-attribute/tree/17.0/product_secondary_unit\n    ```\n  badge4: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/weblate-Translate%20me-F47D42.png\n    :alt: Translate me on Weblate\n    :target: https://translation.odoo-community.org/projects/product-attribute-17-0/product-attribute-17-0-product_secondary_unit\n    ```\n  badge5: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/runboat-Try%20me-875A7B.png\n    :alt: Try me on Runboat\n    :target: https://runboat.odoo-community.org/builds?repo=OCA/product-attribute&target_branch=17.0\n    ```\n  maintainer-sergio-teruel: |-\n    ```{image} https://github.com/sergio-teruel.png?size=40px\n    :alt: sergio-teruel\n    :target: https://github.com/sergio-teruel\n    ```\n---\n\n# Product Secondary Unit\n\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! This file is generated by oca-gen-addon-readme !!\n% !! changes will be overwritten.                   !!\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! source digest: sha256:3038be23ebd37dd87f7595ccf86308fa611b0a81df5134e31c81d12bb79f3f84\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n\n{{ badge1 }} {{ badge2 }} {{ badge3 }} {{ badge4 }} {{ badge5 }}\n\nThis module extends the functionality of product module to allow define\nother units with their conversion factor.\n\n**Table of contents**\n\n```{contents}\n:local: true\n```\n\n## Usage\n\nTo use this module you need to:\n\n1. Go to a *Product > General Information tab*.\n2. Create any record in \"Secondary unit of measure\".\n3. Set the conversion factor.\n\n## Bug Tracker\n\nBugs are tracked on [GitHub Issues](https://github.com/OCA/product-attribute/issues).\nIn case of trouble, please check there if your issue has already been reported.\nIf you spotted it first, help us to smash it by providing a detailed and welcomed\n[feedback](https://github.com/OCA/product-attribute/issues/new?body=module:%20product_secondary_unit%0Aversion:%2017.0%0A%0A**Steps%20to%20reproduce**%0A-%20...%0A%0A**Current%20behavior**%0A%0A**Expected%20behavior**).\n\nDo not contact contributors directly about support or help with technical issues.\n\n## Credits\n\n### Authors\n\n- Tecnativa\n\n### Contributors\n\n- Carlos Dauden \\<<mailto:carlos.dauden@tecnativa.com>>\n- Sergio Teruel \\<<mailto:sergio.teruel@tecnativa.com>>\n- Kitti Upariphutthiphong \\<<mailto:kittiu@ecosoft.co.th>>\n- Pimolnat Suntian \\<<mailto:pimolnats@ecosoft.co.th>>\n- Alan Ramos \\<<mailto:alan.ramos@jarsa.com.mx>>\n\n### Maintainers\n\nThis module is maintained by the OCA.\n\n```{image} https://odoo-community.org/logo.png\n:alt: Odoo Community Association\n:target: https://odoo-community.org\n```\n\nOCA, or the Odoo Community Association, is a nonprofit organization whose\nmission is to support the collaborative development of Odoo features and\npromote its widespread use.\n\nCurrent [maintainer](https://odoo-community.org/page/maintainer-role):\n\n{{ maintainer-sergio-teruel }}\n\nThis module is part of the [OCA/product-attribute](https://github.com/OCA/product-attribute/tree/17.0/product_secondary_unit) project on GitHub.\n\nYou are welcome to contribute. To learn how please visit <https://odoo-community.org/page/Contribute>.\n"], "modules": [{"name": "odoo.addons.product_secondary_unit.models", "documentation": ["License AGPL-3.0 or later (https://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl)."], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "odoo.addons.product_secondary_unit.models.product_product", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.product_secondary_unit.models..product_product", "project": null}}, {"name": "odoo.addons.product_secondary_unit.models.product_second_unit", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.product_secondary_unit.models..product_second_unit", "project": null}}, {"name": "odoo.addons.product_secondary_unit.models.product_secondary_unit_mixin", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.product_secondary_unit.models..product_secondary_unit_mixin", "project": null}}, {"name": "odoo.addons.product_secondary_unit.models.product_template", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.product_secondary_unit.models..product_template", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "odoo.addons.product_secondary_unit.models.product_product", "documentation": ["Copyright 2023 Tecnativa - Sergio Teruel", "License AGPL-3.0 or later (https://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl)."], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "odoo.addons.product_secondary_unit.models.product_product.ProductProduct", "bases": ["models.Model"], "methods": [{"name": "odoo.addons.product_secondary_unit.models.product_product.ProductProduct._compute_secondary_uom_ids", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.product_secondary_unit.models.product_produc